{
  all u,s : User |
    (s in u.follows.follows) 
    and (not u->s in follows) 
    and (u != s) 
    iff s in u.suggested
}

{
  all u1, u3: User | 
    u3 in u1.suggested iff
      (some u2: User | 
        u2 in u1.follows and 
        u3 in u2.follows and 
        u3 !in u1.follows and 
        u1 != u3)
}

{
    all u : User |
        no (u.suggested & u.follows) and
   		u not in u.suggested and
  		all s : u.suggested |
            some f : u.follows | s in f.follows
}

{
  all u1, u2, u3: User | 
    (u2 in u1.follows and          // u1 follows u2
     u3 in u2.follows and          // u2 follows u3
     u3 !in u1.follows and         // u1 doesn't already follow u3
     u1 != u3)                     // u3 is not u1
    implies u3 in u1.suggested     // then u3 should be suggested to u1
}

{
  all u1, u2, u3: User | 
    (u2 in u1.follows and          // u1 follows u2
     u3 in u2.follows and          // u2 follows u3
     u3 !in u1.follows and         // u1 doesn't already follow u3
     u1 != u3)                     // u3 is not u1
    implies u3 in u1.suggested     // then u3 should be suggested to u1
}

{
  all u1, u2, u3: User | 
    (u2 in u1.follows and          // u1 follows u2
     u3 in u2.follows and          // u2 follows u3
     u3 !in u1.follows and         // u1 doesn't already follow u3
     u1 != u3)                     // u3 is not u1
    implies u3 in u1.suggested     // then u3 should be suggested to u1
}

{
	// Suggested are other users followed by followed users, but not yet followed.
all u :User | 
  all uf:User | 
    all us:User |
  	  (u!=uf and uf!=us and
        
        uf in u.follows and 
        us in uf.follows and 
        us not in u.follows)
  
  	   => us in u.suggested
  
  
	
}

{
	// Suggested are other users followed by followed users, but not yet followed.
all u :User | 
  all uf:User | 
    all us:User |
  	  (u!=uf and uf!=us and
        
        uf in u.follows and 
        us in uf.follows and 
        us not in u.follows)
  
  	   <=> us in u.suggested
  
  
	
}

{
	// Suggested are other users followed by followed users, but not yet followed.
all u :User | 
  all uf:User | 
    all us:User |
  	  (u!=uf and uf!=us and
        
        uf in u.follows and 
        us in uf.follows and 
        us not in u.follows)
  
  	   <=> us in u.suggested
  
  
	
}

{
    all u: User, u2: User |
        u != u2 and
        u2 not in u.follows and
        (some u3: u.follows | u2 in u3.follows) implies
        u2 not in u.suggested
}

{
  all u1, u2, u3: User | 
    (u2 in u1.follows and          // u1 follows u2
     u3 in u2.follows and          // u2 follows u3
     u3 !in u1.follows and         // u1 doesn't already follow u3
     u1 != u3)                     // u3 is not u1
    implies u3 = u1.suggested     // then u3 should be suggested to u1
}

{
	// Suggested are other users followed by followed users, but not yet followed.
  	all u1,u2,u3 : User | 
  		u1 != u2 and u1 != u3 and u2 != u3 and
  		u1 not in Influencer and
  		u2 not in Influencer and
  		u3 not in Influencer and
  		u3 in u2.follows and 
  		u2 in u1.follows 
  		implies u3 in suggested.u1
	
}

{
    // Suggested users are those followed by users followed by u1, but not yet followed by u1, and not u1 themselves.
    all u1: User | 
        all u2: User | 
            (u1 in follows.u2) implies 
                (some u3: User | 
                    (u2 in follows.u3) and 
                    not (u3 in follows.u1) and 
                    u3 != u1 and 
                    u3 in u1.suggested)
}
